parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Armadale
definition: The Parish of Armadale consists of Forrestdale, Wungong, Armadale
and Bedfordale.
problems: Update required for new localities in area

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Balcatta/Hamersley
definition: The Parish of Balcatta/Hammersley consists of the
localities of Hamersley, Balcatta and Stirling.

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Bassendean
definition: The Parish of Bassendean consists of the localities of Bassendean,
Ashfield, and that portion of the locality of Bayswater lying to the
east of the line of Gray Street from Walter Road to Collier Road, and
then the line of Jackson Street to Wicks Street, along Wicks Street to
Vincent Street and along Vincent Street to the railway line.
problems: Locality of Bayswater boundary relies on non-existant roads

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Bayswater
definition: The Parish of Bayswater consists of the localities of
Embleton, Bayswater, except that portion lying
to the east of the line of Gray Street From Jackson
Road to Collier Road, the to the line of Jackson
Street to Wicks Street, along Wicks Street to
Vincent Street, and along Vincent Street to the
railway line, together with that portion of Bedford
lying to the south east of Beaufort Street and that
portion of Morley lying to the south and east of Walter
Road.
problems: Locality of Bayswater boundary relies on non-existant roads

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Carine/Duncraig
definition: The Parish of Carine/Duncraig consists of the localities
of Duncraig and Carine.

definition: The Parish of East Perth consists of....

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Ellenbrook
definition: The Parish of Ellenbrook consists of....

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Fremantle
definition: The Parish of Fremantle consists of the localities of Fremantle, North
Fremantle, East Fremantle, Palmyra, Beaconsfield, and that portion of
Hamilton Hill that lies to the west of Carrington Street and north of
Rockingham road.

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Gosnells
definition: The Parish of Gosnells to serve the localities of Gosnells and MArtine, with boundaries as follows:
Northern: Gosnells Road.
Western: Southern Revier.
Eastern: Coinciding with the Eastern boundary of the City of Gosnells.
Southern: Coincinding with the Southern boundary of the City of Gosnells.
problems: Description may not match current localities

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Guildford
definition: The Parish of Guildford consists of South
Guildford, Guildford, Hazelmere, Pyrton and
Caversham.
problems: There is no such place as Pyrton

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Heathridge
definition: The Parish of Heathridge to serve the localities of
Heathridge, Ocean Reef and Connolly.

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Highgate
definition: The Parish of Highgate consists of the locality of
Highgate, and that portion of Perth that lies to the
north of the line drawn through Stuart Street, Monger
Street, and that portion of East Perth which lies
to the north of the line drawn from Edward Street
and Lord Street, and then northwards along Lord Street
along Summer Street, then along Summer Street to the
Swan River, and that portion of Northbridge lying
to the west of Palmerston Street, and that portion
of Mount Lawley lying to the south of a line drawn
along Walcott Street to Alvan Street, then along Alvan
Street, Park Road, along Park Road to Farnley Street,
then along Farnley Street to Almondbury Street, and
then along the line of Almondbury Street across the
railway line to Guildford Road to Ellesmere Street,
then along Ellesmere Street to the river.

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Joondalup
definition: The Parish of Joondalup consists of....

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Kalamunda
definition: The Parish of Kalamunda consists of the localities of
Gooseberry Hill and Kalamunda, within the boundary of
the Shire of Kalamunda

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Kwinana
definition: The Parish of Kwinana consists of the localities of Medina, Orelia, Calista,
Kwinana Town Centre, Naval Base, Kwinana Base, Postans, Hope Valley, The
Spectacles, Mandogalup, Wandi, Anketell, Casuarina, Leda and Wellard.
problems: Kwinana Base should be Kwinana Beach

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Lakelands
definition: The Parish of Lakelands to serve the localities of:-
South Lake (Banjup)
Bibra Lake (Success)
Yangebup (Wattleup)
Jandakot (Munster east of Stock Road)
problems: Localities have changed, description needs update

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Lesmurdie
definition: The Parish of Lesmurdie consists of the localities of
Lesmurdie, Walliston, Bickley, Carmel, Pickering Brook,
within the boundary of the Shire of Kalamunda.

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Lockridge
definition: The Parish of Lockrdige consists of whole of Lockridge.
problems: textual description doesn't include Eden Hill

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Maddington
definition: The Parish of Maddington consists of the localities
of Maddington and Orange Grove, within the City of
Gosnells.

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Maylands
definition: The Parish of Maylands consists of the locality of Maylands
and that portion of Mount Lawley lying to the north east
of Third Avenue to the south west of John Street, and
that portion of Inglewood lying to the south east of John
Street and the line along John Street to Harcourt Road,
and then along Harcourt Road to York Street.

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Mount Lawley
definition: The Parish of Mount Lawley consists of the localities of:
a. Bedford, except for that portion lying to the South
East of Beaufort Street
b. Inglewood, except for that portion lying to the
South East of John Street and that portion bounded
by Dundas Street, Hamer Parade and Walter Road West.
c. Mount Lawley, except for that portion lying to
the North West of Longroyd Street - North Street,
and that portion lying to the South East of John
Street and the North East of Third Avenue.
problems: Mount Lawley gazetted boundary is no longer at Walcott

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Rockingham/Safety Bay
definition: The Parish of Rockingham consists of the localities
of East Rockinham, Rockingham, Peron, Shoalwater,
Safety Bay, Cooloongup, Hillman, Waikiki, Baldivis,
Warnbro and Becher.
problems: no such place as Becher, now Port Kennedy, Warnbro is another parish

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Roleystone
definition: The Parish of Roleystone consists of the localities
of Roleystone, Karragullen and Illawara, as defined
by the postal district boundaries (1987) within the
Town of Armadale
problems: refers to obsolete boundaries, Illawara is now Ashendon

parishes.name: Anglican Parish of Wanneroo
definition: The Parish of Wanneroo/Yanchep consists of the localities of Wannneroo,
Wangarra, Edgewater, Joondalup, Burns, Yanchep, Quinns Rocks, Mariginiup,
and all other localities in the Shire of Wanneroo.
problems: all other localities in Wanneroo not implemented; Burns is now Burns Beach
